or 7+ days. Kills, creates, and promotes have all been PROPOSED but not executed. The pattern of action-item carryover now extends across the full observation window. Sessions are repeating the same analysis (kill v32/v33/v34, pipeline stall) without operator follow-through. Recommend the operator treat the June 2-6 kill batch as a single action (one push of the accumulated strategy-commands.json) rather than evaluating each kill individually.\n",
